ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Fees in Respect of Drugs and Medical Devices Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the FEES IN RESPECT OF DRUGS AND MEDICAL DEVICES REGULATIONS in order to (1) ensure that activities outside of the intended scope of the User Fees Proposal presented by Health Canada to stakeholders and Parliament are not inadvertently subject to these Regulations; and (2) make technical clarifications.
